Package: proxnodefailover
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, iproute2, iputils-ping, isc-dhcp-client, wpasupplicant
Maintainer: Richard Piasentin
Description: Proxmox Node Network Failover
 Keeps a Proxmox node reachable across relocations.
 Supports Wired Static -> Wired DHCP -> Wi-Fi DHCP -> Wired Direct fallback.
 Designed for Tailscale management reachability.
